Small "billing" sample written in Erlang (mnesia, gen_server, mochiweb, erlsom).

Number of test records is defined in src/billing_app.erl (NUM_ACCOUNTS).
Dependencies are: erlang, mochiweb, erlsom.
To compile the sources, run "./compile.sh".
To start the server, run "./start-dev.sh", web ui runs on http://localhost:8080

JSON requests --> http://localhost:8080/json
SOAP requests --> http://localhost:8080/soap
